<item>
            <title>[TEZ-1009] Fixes in log file roll-over</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TEZ-1009</link>
                <project id="12314426" key="TEZ">Apache Tez</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;1) Close the previous file when transferring to a new file&lt;br/&gt;
2) In YARNTezDAGChild use _post for new files to maintain chronological continuity. Currently syslog/stdout/stderr have the contexts in between consecutive tasks.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12706052">TEZ-1009</key>
            <summary>Fixes in log file roll-over</summary>
